{"word":"ἀπαναισχυντέω","slug":"ἀπαναισχυντέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀπαναισχυντέω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἀναίσχυντος'><el>ἀναίσχυντος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to have the effrontery to do</i> or <i>say</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to deny shamelessly</i>, <b><a href='S:Demosthenes'>Dem.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}